<div class="info-box">
    <h2>üó≥Ô∏è New Voting Event Available!</h2>
    <p>Dear {{recipientName}},</p>
    <p>A new voting event has been created and is now available for participation.</p>
</div>

<table class="details-table">
    <tr>
        <th>Event Name</th>
        <td>{{eventName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Description</th>
        <td>{{eventDescription}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Registration Period</th>
        <td>{{registrationStart}} to {{registrationEnd}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Voting Period</th>
        <td>{{votingStart}} to {{votingEnd}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Entry Fee</th>
        <td>{{currency}} {{entryFee}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Categories</th>
        <td>{{categoriesCount}} categories available</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="warning-box">
    <h3>‚è∞ Important Dates</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Registration Deadline:</strong> {{registrationEnd}}</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Deadline:</strong> {{paymentDeadline}}</li>
        <li><strong>Voting Opens:</strong> {{votingStart}}</li>
        <li><strong>Voting Closes:</strong> {{votingEnd}}</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{registrationUrl}}" class="button">Register Now</a>
</p>

{{#if eventDetails}}
<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Event Details</h3>
    <p>{{eventDetails}}</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p>Don't miss this opportunity to participate in the democratic process! Register early to secure your spot.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
{{appName}} Team</p>
